document_data.Notable froghemoths:
[[File:Froghemoth - comic.jpg|thumb|right|''A froghemoth swallowing Salabak.'']]
Froghemoths dwelt in a swamp outside [[Manshaka]] in [[Calimshan]]. In the [[1357 DR|Year of the Prince, 1357 DR]], lured by the fighting between [[Vajra Valmeyjar]] and [[Salabak]], it burst out of the water and caught Salabak with its long tongue, devouring him before retreating underwater.{{Cite comic/The Last Betrayal|19-21}}

Kubazan, one of the [[Primal_spirit#The_Nine_Trickster_Gods_of_Chult|Nine Trickster Gods]] of [[Chult]], was a froghemoth.
